name: Rise Of The Dead:3 Tickets - 25th of January
description:
Rise Of The Dead is here for it's 3rd instalment!! Central Coast's best alternative event is back for it's biggest event to date. This time featuring 8 bands plus a DJ playing all things local between sets and then going as heavy as hell til late. 

Bands include:
Abacination
Darkc3ll
The Takehold 
Trollgasm
Chronolyth 
Pagans Realm 
Na Maza 
Chambers of Insanity

This will be a monster night of amazing live entertainment and not an event to miss.
Doors open at 6pm and it goes til late. Pre-sale tickets can be purchased from any local band for $12 or through the Wise Monkey Entertainment site, otherwise it is $15 on the door.

name: Basemental 2013 Compilation CD
description:
Basemental 2013 is a compilation of tracks from bands who have played at The Basement (Canberra's best venue). There are 20 bands on the cd. There is only a limited pressing of this CD and once it's sold out it's gone forever. Grab yours today!

01. BLEEDING GASOLINE - Set Me Free

name: Bleeding Gasoline 3 Track CD
description: Bleeding Gasoline's debut 3 track single features Leech, Set Me Free & No Religion Here. Recorded at The Grove Studios with one of Australia's best engineers Darren "jENK" Jenkins these 3 tracks have been recorded at a world class level. All tracks were mixed and mastered at Studio 74.
